{"tid":1060223,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"3D係唔係已經廢了?","createTime":"2019-03-13T15:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T19:21:30.000Z","uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2532fadef5f582adce86f1266d719df2a7a38b7f","tid":1060223,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"至於 3D Vision 圖形技術，NVIDIA在另一篇文章中表示：&ldquo;在2019年4月發布Release 418版本的最終驅動程式後GeForce Game Ready將不再支援NVIDIA 3D Vision 產品NVIDIA支援團隊將繼續解決3D Vision的關鍵驅動問題到2020年4月，日後希望使用3D Vision的用家可以繼續使用Release 418版本驅動程式。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA在2009 年發佈3D Vision，讓玩家在PC上體驗最高質量的3D立體效果，當時 3D Vision 生態系統曾贏得1000多種不同產品的加盟，涉及GPU繪圖卡、筆記本、桌面台式機、顯示器、電視機、投影儀、攝像機、視頻應用程序、遊戲等等多種類別，然而 NVIDIA 放棄再為3D Vision圖形技術提供驅動程式支援，這似乎默認了3D Vision根本沒有流行起來。"},{"pid":"fa4977a89eb0a1e90db6c270587befc736aad565","tid":1060223,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"咁多年都搞唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a7fda6db11347febe72a1b996812b48f0d7779","tid":1060223,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔睇呢個post都唔知有啲咁嘅野"},{"pid":"4662d71ba039002f63f7f6d030d677e3f7b8687e","tid":1060223,"uid":236227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:05:56.000Z","msg":"開頭都係得少少搞頭 但搞左排無乜人搞得起就收左皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd04ab612dabd1d42efcffd5a854e4ebabdbb6eb","tid":1060223,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"vr既過渡品"},{"pid":"c2c1fb56d630cfbaf80c46fa1e2aeadf2a71779e","tid":1060223,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9a7fda6db11347febe72a1b996812b48f0d7779","tid":1060223,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔睇呢個post都唔知有啲咁嘅野"},"c